Treasury balances at the FederalReserve fell on April 10 to 3.373 billion dlrs from 3.523billion dlrs on the previous business day, the Treasury said inits latest budget statement.    Balances in tax and loan note accounts fell to 11.645billion dlrs from 11.869 billion dlrs on the same respectivedays.    The Treasury's operating cash balance totaled 15.018billion dlrs compared with 15.392 billion dlrs on April 9. Reuter&#3;